      "headline": "Cloud Cost Optimization: A Senior Engineer's Lens on the Bill",
      "deck": "Cost is a non-functional requirement you trade against reliability and velocity, not a virtue you chase to zero.",
      "datePublished": "2026-06-09",
      "dateModified": "2026-06-09",
      "readingTime": "15 min",
